# Mobis Market Update Generator

Automated M&A market update generator — deploys to Vercel in ~2 minutes, no installation needed.

## Deploy to Vercel (free, no admin access required)

### Step 1 — Put the files on GitHub
1. Go to https://github.com and sign in (or create a free account)
2. Click **New repository** → name it `mobis-generator` → click **Create repository**
3. Upload all files from this folder: drag them into the GitHub file upload area

### Step 2 — Deploy on Vercel
1. Go to https://vercel.com and sign in with your GitHub account
2. Click **Add New → Project**
3. Select your `mobis-generator` repository → click **Deploy**

### Step 3 — Add your API key
1. In Vercel, go to your project → **Settings → Environment Variables**
2. Add: `ANTHROPIC_API_KEY` = your key from https://console.anthropic.com
3. Click **Redeploy** (Settings → Deployments → Redeploy)

Your app is live at `https://mobis-generator.vercel.app` (or similar URL Vercel assigns).

## Usage
1. Select quarter + year → click **Scan for deals**
2. Claude searches all 11 sources, counts deals for current AND prior year automatically
3. Add the deals you want to highlight
4. Click **Generate commentary** → Mobis-style text streams in
5. Click **Build PowerPoint** → `.pptx` downloads directly
